timelineItems.desc: The Vancouver Whitecaps and Real Salt Lake face off at BC Place in a vital Western Conference match-up with only 3 points separating the two teams in the standings.
timelineItems.title: KICKOFF: Vancouver Whitecaps vs Real Salt Lake | May 30, 2015

timelineItems.name: Janice Meehan
timelineItems.text: Beautifully day for a soccer game. The roof is open #vwfc http://t.co/IDBSuwbWOf

timelineItems.name: Steve V
timelineItems.text: Koffie, Ousted, Laba terrific for #VWFC

timelineItems.name: BCSoccerweb.com
timelineItems.text: FULL TIME! The Caps are ready to hit the road in style with a well deserved 2-1 win over #RSL who seem to be bugged by something.

timelineItems.name: Tyler Green
timelineItems.text: FT as #VWFC beat #RSL 2-1 on goals from Koffie and Techera. Koffie was named #MoTM #VANvRSL

timelineItems.name: Sean Cruz
timelineItems.text: #RSL coach running right to the referees right after the match to give them an earful, before shaking hands with Robbo.

timelineItems.name: Major League Soccer
timelineItems.text: FT: A Gershon Koffie stunner helps lift @WhitecapsFC over @RealSaltLake, 2-1: http://t.co/0KElHnChnL #VANvRSL http://t.co/Av8NMYXPMt

timelineItems.name: DKH
timelineItems.text: Solid game from Vancouver not only did we win but we deserved it #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Derek Rawlings
timelineItems.text: That's 3 points in the book, and a fairly lopsided game. Well done by our #vwfc. Undefeated on the new pitch!

timelineItems.name: Vancouver Whitecaps
timelineItems.text: You can tell it's warm out there, as Robbo has opted to go sweater-less for the match. #VWFC #VANvRSL

timelineItems.name: Charles Barnard

timelineItems.name: Ryan Lehal
timelineItems.text: It's still early, but boy does Mauro look lively #WhitecapsFC #VWFC

timelineItems.text: .@WhitecapsFC the better of the two sides through the first 25'. There be a goal comin' soon I think... #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: My concern with Jaime is not that he is not scoring goals. It is that he is not taking shots. Only 2 in 230 min. played. #RSL #RSLStats

timelineItems.name: Amelia
timelineItems.text: I should count this @WhitecapsFC game as a workout because my heart is racing! So much action! #VWFC

timelineItems.name: Wayne Outram

timelineItems.text: GOOOOOOAAAAALLLL A BEAUTY FROM KOFFIE!!! 1-0 #VWFC

timelineItems.text: Even Sepp Blatter wouldn't win an election against that Gershon Koffie strike. Caps up 1-0. #VWFC #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: GERSHON____ GERSHON____ GERSHON____ #thankyou #VWFC #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: What a goal from Gershon Koffie. #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: .@realsaltlake in danger of being overrun. Needs a half time rethink for Cassar. #VANvRSL

timelineItems.name: Steve Corpuz
timelineItems.text: Javiiiiiiiiiii! #RSL

timelineItems.name: Matt Robinson
timelineItems.text: EL MAESTRO!!!!!!! #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: What a goal!! #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: That's the half. It's 1-1 here at @BCPlace #VWFC #VANvRSL

timelineItems.text: HT 1-1 between #VANvRSL. Two jaw dropping goals.
